i want to apply for the "Ad credit feature" on my account.

To apply for the Ad credit feature on your account, you need to add your credit card information and purchase ad credits to fund your account. If you are an international advertiser and not eligible for postpay, you can wire funds to us, and we will add credits to your account once we confirm the wire. For more details on where to send the wire, please refer to this document: [newsbreak FAQ](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/34801428495373-How-to-integrate-with-Digistore24).
